.","type":"text"}]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The method allows the user to provide a data ID, which will be returned as the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dataId"},{"text":" parameter in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"type":"text","text":" event. However, it’s important to note that multiple partial updates can be queued"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"for the same GeoJSON source when ongoing source parsing is taking place. In these cases, the partial"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"updates will be applied to the source in batches. Only the data ID provided in the most recent call within","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"each batch will be included in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"text":" event. If no data ID is provided in the most recent","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"call, the data ID in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"type":"text","text":"event will be null."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Note"},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleError","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" if there is a problem removing features from the source.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Throws","style":"note"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/Overview","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/Style","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleManager"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/stylemanager\/removegeojsonsourcefeatures(forsourceid:featur